title: Drivers Universally Praise NASCAR's 2016 Rules Package
text:
Topix › Sports › Drivers Universally Praise NASCAR's 2... Drivers Universally Praise NASCAR's 2016 Rules Package Next Story Prev Story 9 min ago Read more: ABC News 
Joey Logano had a one-word response when asked for his thoughts on the low-downforce rules package that NASCAR approved for next season: "Great.""I think it's exactly what we want," said Logano, the only driver already guaranteed a spot in the next round of the Chase after his victory last weekend at Charlotte.
